modName: All Perfect Susanoo's for Uchiha Clan
descriptionHtml:
[color=#ff0000][size=6]UPDATED FOR UCHIHA CLAN 2.0 BE SURE TO READ THE FIRST STICKY POST, FEW IMPORTANT CHANGES[/size][/color]




I decided it's finally time and it will be better if I merge all of my mods into 1 mod page.


This mod is an add-on for the main mod [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51136/?]UchihaClan[/url] and will add Perfect Susanoo for the rest of the paths. It will also add stages 1,2,3 for Obito and Shisui. Im bad at writing scripts, so to get every spell/weapon in this mod, you will have to use console, just saying.
It will also add combination of Sasuke's EMS and his Rinnegan
I also decided to change 9 tomoed red/purple rinnegan to 6 tomoed rinnegan, so it looks more like in manga/anime. You can check it at the last page of pictures.
[color=#9900ff][size=6]
Sasuke's Perfect Susanoo
[img]http://i.imgur.com/JOH0WSi.jpg[/img]
[/size][/color][b][u][size=4]Mods that are required before installing :
[/size]Install in this order : 
[/u][/b]
[list=1]
[*][size=2][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51136/?]Original The Uchiha Clan Mod[/url][/size] and it's requirements.
[*][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/31229/?]Armor mod[/url] 
[*][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/24704/?]Armor mod 2[/url]
[*][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/53271/?]Wings mod 1[/url]  
[*][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/57646/?]Wings mod 2[/url] - the version you need to download is - [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/download/1000146043]Soul Hound Pack V1.2[/url](overwrite everything from first wings mod while installing and ingame Susanoo's wings will be "Snow Wings".
[/list][list=1]
[u]
For Bijuu version also : [/u]
[/list]
[list=1]
[*][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/59335/?]Dragonslayer Bow and Siege Arrows[/url]
[*][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/8654/?]Magic Arrows[/url]
[*][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/39815/?]Berserk Grunberd Armor[/url]
[/list]

[size=4]Optional Mods:[/size]


[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/64718/?]Flying Mod Overhauled and Enhanced[/url] - After you installed in game use power called "flying configuration" go to collisions and turn them off.

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/37347/?]Customizable Camera[/url] - if you set PS scale to 500% and you want to be able to see it just like in my video, you have to download this and configure it like [url=http://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/mods/110/images/68637-0-1439465870.jpg]here[/url]
Now finally you can download and install my mod. Overwrite everything you'll be asked for.

[i][color=#ffff00][size=5]How to use it?[/size][/color]
[/i]
Open console and type "help perfect" and search for the "Sasuke's Perfect Susanoo" spell. Then use "player.addspell ID". 
[size=4]You have to SCROLL UP through the console with "PageUp" button on your keyboard to find this spell
[/size](same goes for "PageDown" if you want to scroll down)

You can now also use any spell/shout while in Susanoo form and equip any weapon you want. Also you can equip some types of armor but there's not too many.
You can only equip things that does not affect the main body so obviously you can't equip any armor, boots or gauntlets but you can wear stuff like cowls or capes/cloaks but they will be normal looking and won't get this purple chakra looking. 

[color=#ffff00][size=4]How to get Wings ? 
[/size][/color]
Open console type "help mutagen" and search for the spell called "Mutagen : Control Snow Dragon Wings". Then use "player.addspell ID". 


[color=#ffff00][size=4]How to get susanoo blades ?[/size][/color]

Open console and search for items called "Sasuke's Perfect Susanoo Blade 1H/2H" use command player.additem ID count


[u][size=4]For Bijuu version :[/size]
[/u]

Open console and type [font=Georgia][i]help dragonslayer[/i] [/font]search for the item called "Dragonslayer Bow" and use command [i][font=Trebuchet MS]player.additem id cout[/font]
[/i]
[color=#ffff00][size=4]How to get Arrows?[/size][/color]

Open console and type help [i]"storm arrows" and use command [i][font=Trebuchet MS]player.additem id cout
